<div class="landing-page">
    <section class="features" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
        <div class="features__content">
            <h2 class="features__title">Privacy Policy</h2>
            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left;">
                <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: left;">
                    <h3>Data Collection</h3>
                    <p>FlightTracker collects only the information necessary to provide you with flight tracking services. This includes flight details you manually enter, basic account information, and usage analytics to improve our service.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Data Usage</h3>
                    <p>Your flight data is used solely for providing tracking services, generating statistics, and creating your digital aviation passport. We do not sell or share your personal flight information with third parties.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Data Security</h3>
                    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. All data transmission is encrypted, and we regularly update our security practices.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Your Rights</h3>
                    <p>You have the right to access, modify, or delete your data at any time through your account settings. You can also export your flight data in CSV format.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Contact</h3>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our support channels.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn--primary">Back to Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>